<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١٢٣٦ - حَدَّثَنَا وَكِيعٌ،<span class="c5"> عَنْ شُعْبَةَ قَالَ:</span> سَأَلْتُ الْحَكَمَ، وَحَمَّادًا عَنْ بَوْلِ الشَّاةِ،<span class="c5"> فَقَالَ حَمَّادٌ:</span> <span class="c2">«يُغْسَلُ»</span>،<span class="c5"> وَقَالَ الْحَكَمُ:</span> <span class="c2">«لَا»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>